{{extend 'layout_new.html'}}
<html>
<head>
  <title>PERT - Products</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="PERTCSS.css">
 <style>
      header {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: transparent;
        padding: 10px;
      }
  
      nav ul {
        background-color: transparent;
        list-style-type: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
  
      nav ul li {
        margin-right: 10px;
      }
  
      nav ul li a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #333;
        padding: 5px;
      }
  
      /* Custom CSS for the home button */
      .home-button {
        width: 70px; /* Adjust the width as desired */
        height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
      }
      
      footer {
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
      }
      
      .carousel-item {
        display: relative;
      }
  
      .carousel-item img {
        object-fit: cover;
        flex: 1;
      }
  
      .carousel-item .carousel-caption {
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Adjust the background color and opacity as needed */
        color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        width: 100%; /* Adjust the width as needed */
        height: 60%;
        border-radius: 20px;
      }
  
          /* Styling for the products section */
          .products {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-around;
      }
  
      /* Styling for product items */
      .product {
        width: 300px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding: 10px;
        border: 0px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
  
      /* Styling for product images */
      .product img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
  
      /* Styling for product names */
      .product h3 {
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
          /* Custom CSS for the login form */
    .login-container {
        max-width: 400px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
  
      .login-container h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
  
      .login-container input[type="text"],
      .login-container input[type="password"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }
  
      .login-container button[type="submit"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 3px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      body {
        background-image: url("images/Farm.jpeg");
        background-size: cover; /* Adjust to your preference */
      }
      a {
        color: #e6440e;
      }
      a:visited {
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      a:hover {
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      a:active {
        color: #e6440e;
      }

      
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  
  <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="../static/images/Cornfield.jpeg" alt="image of a corn field">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3></h3>
          <p>"Food security is at the heart of our purpose. We tirelessly research and develop resilient crops and alternative protein sources to sustainably nourish the populace in the midst of scarcity. Through responsible land management and localized production, we foster self-sufficiency and reduce reliance on unreliable supply chains.

            Waste management is not a luxury; it is a necessity. We strive to eliminate waste through comprehensive recycling and upcycling programs, utilizing every available resource to its fullest potential. Our packaging solutions are designed to minimize environmental impact, ensuring that our commitment to sustainability extends from farm to table.
            
            We understand that our responsibility extends beyond our operations. We actively engage with local communities, partnering with organizations to empower and support initiatives that promote sustainable farming, equitable access to food, and resilient communities. We prioritize ethical practices, ensuring the fair treatment of our employees and the protection of their well-being."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100"  src="../static/images/tomato.jpeg" alt="image of a tomatoe plant">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3></h3>
          <p>"At PERT, we deeply believe in the power of sustainability. We understand that the choices we make today shape the world we'll inherit tomorrow. That's why we are committed to integrating sustainable practices into every aspect of our operations. From sourcing ethically and locally grown ingredients to minimizing waste through innovative production methods, sustainability is at the core of our business.

            We strive to reduce our environmental footprint by implementing energy-efficient technologies, optimizing packaging materials, and supporting renewable energy sources. Our commitment extends beyond our products to the communities we serve, as we actively engage in initiatives that promote environmental education and conservation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img class="d-block w-100" src="../static/images/Plant.jpeg" alt="image of a plant sprouting">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h3></h3>
          <p>At PERT, our mission is to forge a sustainable future in the face of adversity. As a dystopian food company, we recognize the urgent need to provide nourishment while preserving the fragile resources of our desolate world. We are dedicated to pioneering sustainable practices that ensure the survival and well-being of both humanity and the environment.

            Our commitment to sustainability drives every aspect of our operations. We embrace resource efficiency, optimizing the use of scarce resources and minimizing waste in our production processes. By harnessing innovative technologies, we maximize the yield of our limited agricultural spaces, cultivating nutrient-rich food with minimal environmental impact.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 PERT Food Distribution</p>
  </footer>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
